Package: STMPlotTools
Title: Set of plotting functions
Version: 1.2
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Emanuele", family = "Fabbiani", email = "donlelef@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person( given = "Claudio", family = "Peroni", role = "aut"))
Description: This package lets you plot effective surface, scatter plot and matrix plot. Its main purpose is to present wafer fault maps and the result of KDE and SOM algorithms.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.3)
Imports: RColorBrewer, STMFaultPattern, kohonen, plot3D
